Bit Innovate is an Australian owned initiative promoting Bitcoin and providing innovative services to the Bitcoin community.

Bit Innovates first offering was its Buy Bitcoins service which facilitates the purchase of Bitcoins with Australian Dollars (AUD) by accepting cash deposits at a Bank branch. This fast and easy to use local service resolves the need for individuals to send money overseas to international Bitcoin exchanges, by providing a safe and legal way to buy Bitcoins in Australia.


##Buy Bitcoins

###AUD

* Cash deposit at any Commonwealth Bank.

###NZD

* Cash deposit at any ASB (coming soon!)


